description: The enumeration of possible FormData submission states.
name: StateEnum

enum.name: WAITING_FOR_SUBMISSION
enum.description: Indicates that the FormData is waiting for the creator to submit it.

enum.name: SUBMITTED_WAITING_FOR_REVIEW
enum.description: Indicates the FormData has been submitted and is now awaiting review.

enum.name: ACCEPTED
enum.description: The submitted FormData has been reviewed and accepted.

enum.name: REJECTED
enum.description: The submitted FormData has been reviewed but was not accepted.  See the reason for more details.
